    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from documented subframe reinforcement and refreshed bushings. Recent service includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and precision valve adjustment, ensuring the high-revving powerplant operates at peak efficiency. Equipped with a factory limited-slip differential and staggered Style 67 wheels, this example offers a visceral, analog driving experience. While it shows minor cosmetic patina consistent with a well-loved driver, it remains mechanically robust and track-capable.",
